These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: superhero, spy, mystery
1. the person watching superhero movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching superhero movies is not to the left of the person watching spy movies##8
3. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching spy movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |    3     |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | spy | superhero |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, hot-chocolate, cola
1. the person drinking cola is not to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##8
2. the person drinking cola is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3     |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | cola | hot-chocolate |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-3::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, october, july
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in july##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |  3  |
| Birthday   | october | march | july |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-4::.
3 different games are played: go, backgammon, bridge
1. the person playing backgammon is not to the left of the person playing bridge##8
2. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |  2   |      3      |
| Game   | bridge | backgammon | go |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-5::.
