2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##5
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is not to the right of the person who's sport is cricket##8

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |     2      |   3   |
| Sport   | weightlifting | water-polo | cricket |

 